						Chernobyl Children Cancer Care Cardiff (The 5Cs) is a non political, non denominational, Cardiff
						based charity that is officially twinned with the <a href="http://en.hospice.by/" target="_blank">Belarusian Childrenâ€™s Hospice</a> in Minsk, Belarus.
